<P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#000000><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/usouleach.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Souleach</A></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Eternal Valor/Intrepid Spirit</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>posts: </FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>5</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#FFFF00>2/27/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#FFFF00>11:15:20 am</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT><BR><img src=http:/www.geocities.com/eqsells/souleach.jpg http:/www.geocities.com/eqsells/souleach.jpg width = 250 height = 175></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B>&nbsp;<FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re: Indy day questions</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">ok lost me what is indy day does this mean if my guid is in fear and cazic is up we do not get to kill him that a epic guild can come in and kill ?? if so how am i suppose to finish my epic quest that i am working on as well. I am just trying to understand. I will keep looking around for mor info on this indy day.<br>
